---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LandingNav from '../components/LandingNav.astro';
import LandingFooter from '../components/LandingFooter.astro';
---

<Layout title="Acerca de AGROVELAS">
  <LandingNav current="/acerca" />

  <section class="py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #022c22 0%, #064e3b 40%, #047857 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">Acerca de AGROVELAS</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-100/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Transformando la gestion ganadera en las comunidades altoandinas del Peru mediante tecnologia accesible y datos confiables.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Mision</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-4">Nuestra Mision</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Desarrollar un sistema digital que facilite el registro, monitoreo y control de animales mediante el uso de tecnologias accesibles, permitiendo a los productores tomar decisiones basadas en informacion confiable, incluso en entornos con conectividad limitada.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Vision</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-4">Nuestra Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Convertirnos en la herramienta integral y escalable de referencia para la gestion pecuaria en el Peru, incorporando progresivamente tecnologias como IoT, geolocalizacion y analisis de datos para optimizar la produccion y mejorar la calidad de vida de los productores agropecuarios.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">El contexto</h2>
      <div class="max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">El sector agropecuario en las regiones altoandinas del Peru, especialmente en Cusco, enfrenta multiples desafios relacionados con la gestion y control de animales de campo. El uso de metodos tradicionales de registro, la falta de seguimiento continuo y la limitada adopcion de tecnologias dificultan la toma de decisiones informadas.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">AGROVELAS nace del levantamiento de informacion mediante entrevistas a actores del sector (veterinarios, ganaderos, zootecnistas) y de la identificacion de sus necesidades reales: un sistema que funcione con o sin internet, que sea facil de usar y que centralice toda la informacion del ganado.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">El sistema esta diseñado para alpacas, llamas, ovejas, bovinos y caprinos, las principales especies de la ganaderia altoandina.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FASES DEL PROYECTO -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 text-xs font-semibold mb-4">Roadmap</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Fases del proyecto</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 max-w-xl mx-auto">Nuestra hoja de ruta para transformar la ganaderia altoandina</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-10 sm:pl-12">
        <!-- linea vertical -->
        <div class="absolute left-4 sm:left-5 top-2 bottom-2 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-300 via-blue-300 to-purple-300"></div>

        <!-- Fase 1 -->
        <div class="relative mb-10 last:mb-0">
          <div class="absolute -left-6 sm:-left-7 top-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 border-2 border-white shadow flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">Fase 1</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-600 bg-green-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">Completado</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Beta inicial</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Registro digital centralizado de animales con datos fenotipicos, sanitarios (peso, DTE, diagnostico) y reproductivos. Trazabilidad con codigos QR individuales.</p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-xs font-medium">Registro</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-xs font-medium">Sanidad</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-xs font-medium">QR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fase 2 -->
        <div class="relative mb-10 last:mb-0">
          <div class="absolute -left-6 sm:-left-7 top-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border-2 border-white shadow flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">Fase 2</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">En progreso</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Expansion IoT</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Integracion de sensores GPS para geolocalizacion en tiempo real, collares inteligentes con monitoreo de salud y alertas automaticas por comportamiento anomalo.</p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-medium">GPS</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-medium">Sensores</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-medium">Alertas</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-1.5 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="bg-blue-500 h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all" style="width:55%;"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">55% completado</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fase 3 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-6 sm:-left-7 top-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 border-2 border-white shadow flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-600 bg-purple-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">Fase 3</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 bg-purple-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">Proximo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Escalabilidad & IA</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Analisis predictivo con inteligencia artificial para deteccion temprana de enfermedades, optimizacion de reproduccion y alimentacion. Expansion a nuevas regiones del Peru.</p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-xs font-medium">IA</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-xs font-medium">Predictivo</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-xs font-medium">Escalar</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EQUIPO -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 text-xs font-semibold mb-4">Equipo</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Conocenos</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 max-w-xl mx-auto">Detras de AGROVELAS hay un equipo comprometido con la innovacion rural</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Gustavo Jhon -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden ring-4 ring-brand-100">
            <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/100982198?v=4" alt="Gustavo Jhon" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Gustavo Jhon</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-600 font-medium mb-2">@hustavojhon</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Full-stack & fundador</p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex justify-center gap-3">
            <a href="https://github.com/HustavoJhon" target="_blank" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-700 transition-colors" aria-label="GitHub">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rodrigo Sevillanos -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-200 flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-blue-100">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">RS</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Rodrigo Sevillanos</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium mb-2">Front End</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Desarrollo de interfaz de usuario y experiencia de producto</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Gabriel -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-purple-200 flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-purple-100">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">GA</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Gabriel</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium mb-2">Inteligencia Artificial</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Modelos predictivos y analisis de datos para deteccion temprana</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Yornet -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-100 to-amber-200 flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-amber-100">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">YO</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Yornet</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium mb-2">Base de Datos</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Diseno y optimizacion de bases de datos para el sistema</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <LandingFooter />
</Layout>
